Sum of array elements

Write a  program to find the sum of elements in an array.

Sample Input:

3
1
2
3

Sample Output:
6

Code :

import java.util.*;
public class Sumarray
{
    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
        int n=sc.nextInt();
        int arr[]=new int[n];
        int sum=0;
        for(int i=1;i<=n;i++)
        {
            int b=sc.nextInt();
            sum=sum+b;
        }
        System.out.println(sum);
    }
}
